<lb n="0424b06"/><head type="no">No. 1306</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0424b07"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0424034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】享保年間刊豐山大學藏本，【甲】久安四年寫仁和寺藏本，【乙】久安五年寫高山寺藏本，【丙】文和二年寫高野山寶壽院藏本</note>北斗七星護摩祕要儀<note n="0424035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">軌＋（一卷）【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0424035"><lem>軌</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">軌一卷</rdg></app></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0424b08"/>
<lb n="0424b09"/><byline type="Author">大興善寺翻經院灌頂阿闍梨述</byline>
<lb n="0424b10"/><p><note n="0424036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（或本佛言）＋我【丙】</note><app n="0424036"><lem>我</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">或本佛言我</rdg></app>今為末世薄福眾生故。說是北極七星供
<lb n="0424b11"/>養護摩次第儀則。於<note n="0424037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">靜＝淨&M062403;【甲】</note><app n="0424037"><lem>靜</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【甲】">淨</rdg></app>室中作一水壇。或
<lb n="0424b12"/><note n="0424038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">方或圓＝圓或方【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0424038"><lem>方或圓</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">圓或方</rdg></app>各足一肘。以茅香甘松熏<note n="0424039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">陸＋（白交）【甲】，（白）【乙】</note><app n="0424039"><lem>陸</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">陸白交</rdg><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">陸白</rdg></app>龍腦
<lb n="0424b13"/>白檀五味和合泥塗之。其壇<note n="0424040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">場＝即【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0424040"><lem>場</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">即</rdg></app>內安著圓爐。
<lb n="0424b14"/>飲食果子<note n="0424041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（七）＋分【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0424041"><lem>分</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">七分</rdg></app>別置<note n="0424042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">之燒＝燒之【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0424042"><lem>之。燒</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">燒之</rdg></app>食謂<note n="0424043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">飯食＝粥飯腦【甲】，飯腦【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0424043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">飯食＝粥飯腦【甲】，＝飯腦【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0424043"><lem>飯食</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">粥飯腦</rdg><rdg wit="【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">飯腦</rdg></app>果餅
<lb n="0424b15"/><note n="0424044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">酥＝蘇【甲】【乙】＊</note><app n="0424044"><lem>酥</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">蘇</rdg></app>蜜等。但五穀并乳木。隨人命星相<note n="0424045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">撿＝換【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0424045"><lem>撿</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">換</rdg></app>
<lb n="0424b16"/>用之</p>
<lb n="0424b17"/><p>先啟詞曰　至心奉啟北極七<note n="0424046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔明〕－【甲】</note><app n="0424046"><lem>明</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0424047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">娜＝那【甲】，〔娜〕－【乙】</note><app n="0424047"><lem>娜</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">那</rdg><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>羅貪
<lb n="0424b18"/><note n="0424048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔狼〕－【丙】</note><app n="0424048"><lem>狼</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0424049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">巨＝臣【乙】</note><app n="0424049"><lem>巨</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">臣</rdg></app>門祿存文曲廉貞武曲破軍尊星。為
<lb n="0424b19"/><note n="0424050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">陀＝施&M062485;【原】，施【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0424050" resp="CBETA" type="mod">陀＝施&M062485;【原】，＝施【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0424050"><lem><sic corr="施" resp="【原】">陀</sic></lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">施</rdg></app>主<note n="0424051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">某甲二字甲乙二本作夾註</note><note n="0424051" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（某甲）二字本文＝（某甲）二字夾註【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0424051"><lem>某甲</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho"><note place="inline">某甲</note></rdg></app>。災厄解脫壽命延長得見百秋。
<lb n="0424b20"/>今作曼<note n="0424052" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">荼＝茶【甲】</note><app n="0424052"><lem>荼</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">茶</rdg></app>羅。唯願垂哀降臨此處。納受護
<lb n="0424b21"/>摩。擁護施主<note n="0424053" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">某甲二字甲乙二本作夾註</note><note n="0424053" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（某甲）二字本文＝（某甲）二字夾註【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0424053"><lem>某甲</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho"><note place="inline">某甲</note></rdg></app>。災難解脫壽命增長所願
<lb n="0424b22"/>從心<note place="inline">三<note n="0424054" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">遍＝反【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0424054"><lem>遍</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">反</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0424b23"/><p>次結其印。虛心合掌。以二大指。捻二無名
<lb n="0424b24"/>指甲。<note n="0424055" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔二〕－【丙】</note><app n="0424055"><lem>二</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>中指二小指如蓮葉。二頭指小開
<lb n="0424b25"/>屈來去</p>
<lb n="0424b26"/><p>次誦一字頂輪王真言。并召北斗七星真言</p>
<lb n="0424b27"/><p>頂<note n="0424056" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">輪＋（王）【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0424056"><lem>輪</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">輪王</rdg></app>真言曰</p>
<lb n="0424b28"/><p type="dharani"><note n="0424057" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">甲乙丙三本俱梵字無之</note><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5A9;</t><t lang="chi">曩</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5ED;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0424058" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">慕＝謨【甲】【乙】，莫【丙】</note><note n="0424058" resp="CBETA" type="mod">慕＝謨【甲】【乙】，＝莫【丙】</note><app n="0424058"><lem>慕</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">謨</rdg><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">莫</rdg></app></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A67A;</t><t lang="chi">三</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5E5;</t><t lang="chi">曼</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-CA56;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0424059" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">多＝哆【甲】【乙】＊</note><app n="0424059"><lem>多</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">哆</rdg></app></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A56F;</t><t lang="chi">那</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5FD;</t><t lang="chi">羅</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd"><app><lem>&SD-A56F;&SD-A5FD;</lem><rdg wit="【大】">&SD-D957;</rdg></app></t><t lang="chi">那羅</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5B5;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0424060" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">跛＝破【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0424060"><lem>跛</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">破</rdg></app></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A47C;</t><t lang="chi">左</t></tt>
<lb n="0424b29"/>
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1306.0424c" n="0424c"/>
<lb n="0424c01"/><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5FD;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0424061" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">囉＝羅【甲】【乙】＊</note><app n="0424061"><lem>囉</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">羅</rdg></app></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E17C;</t><t lang="chi">吽</t></tt></p>
<lb n="0424c02"/>
<lb n="0424c03"/><p>召北斗真言曰</p>
<lb n="0424c04"/><p type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5A9;</t><t lang="chi">曩</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5F0;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0424062" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">莫＝謨【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0424062"><lem>莫</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">謨</rdg></app></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A67A;</t><t lang="chi">三</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5E5;</t><t lang="chi">曼</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-CA56;</t><t lang="chi"><app type="＊" source="0424059"><lem>多</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">哆</rdg></app></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A56F;</t><t lang="chi">那</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5FD;</t><t lang="chi">羅</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5A9;</t><t lang="chi">曩</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-CFCF;</t><t lang="chi">翳</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E0AF;</t><t lang="chi">醯</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A6AA;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0424063" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">呬＝枳【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0424063"><lem>呬</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">枳</rdg></app></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5B5;</t><t lang="chi">頗</t></tt>
<lb n="0424c05"/>
<lb n="0424c06"/><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-CFC7;</t><t lang="chi">伊</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A6A8;</t><t lang="chi">賀</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-CFC7;</t><t lang="chi">伊</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A56F;</t><t lang="chi">那</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-CFC7;</t><t lang="chi">伊</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A440;</t><t lang="chi">迦</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-CFC7;</t><t lang="chi">伊</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5FD;</t><t lang="chi"><app type="＊" source="0424061"><lem>囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">羅</rdg></app></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-CFC7;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0424064" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔伊〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0424064"><lem>伊</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-AAF4;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>謨<app type="＊" source="0424061"><lem>囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">羅</rdg></app></zi><sg><note n="0424065" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔二合〕－【乙】</note><app n="0424065"><lem>二合</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></sg></yin></t></tt>
<lb n="0424c07"/>
<lb n="0424c08"/><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A557;</t><t lang="chi">哆</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5FD;</t><t lang="chi"><app type="＊" source="0424061"><lem>囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">羅</rdg></app></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A464;</t><t lang="chi">伽</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5FD;</t><t lang="chi"><app type="＊" source="0424061"><lem>囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">羅</rdg></app></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A6B2;</t><t lang="chi">唅</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-DA49;</t><t lang="chi">娑<note n="0424066" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00085;＋（二合）夾註【甲】</note><app n="0424066"><lem>&CB00085;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note></rdg></app></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A6A9;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0424067" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">訶＝賀【甲】【丙】，賀引【乙】</note><note n="0424067" resp="CBETA" type="mod">訶＝賀【甲】【丙】，＝賀引【乙】</note><app n="0424067"><lem>訶</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【丙】" resp="Taisho">賀</rdg><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">賀引</rdg></app></t></tt></p>
<lb n="0424c09"/>
<lb n="0424c10"/><p>以手<note n="0424068" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">取＋（命）【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0424068"><lem>取</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">取命</rdg></app>木及穀并<app type="＊" source="0424044"><lem>酥</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">蘇</rdg></app><note n="0424069" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蜜＝密【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0424069"><lem>蜜</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">密</rdg></app>油等。擲之於爐內
<lb n="0424c11"/>火燒之。<note n="0424070" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">自＝目【甲】</note><app n="0424070"><lem>自</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">目</rdg></app>專視其本命之星。若動搖變色。
<lb n="0424c12"/><note n="0424071" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔光照通〕－【丙】</note><app n="0424071"><lem>光<note n="0424072" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔照通〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0424072"><lem>照通</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>爍<note n="0424073" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">光貌＝光色&M062485;【原】，〔光貌〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0424073"><lem><sic corr="光色" resp="【原】">光貌</sic></lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>黃白者。<note n="0424074" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">即＋（為）【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0424074"><lem>即</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">即為</rdg></app>應願如<note n="0424075" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">來＝未即【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0424075"><lem>來</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">未即</rdg></app>依
<lb n="0424c13"/>前法七日夜而為之。必應如事不即其星藏
<lb n="0424c14"/>沒不見<note place="inline">決云<note n="0424076" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">不＋（可）【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0424076"><lem>不</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">不可</rdg></app>求也</note>謂北斗七星者日月五星之精
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1306.0425a" n="0425a"/>
<lb n="0425a01"/>也。曩括七曜照臨八方上曜於天神下直于
<lb n="0425a02"/>人間。以司善惡而分禍福。群星所朝宗萬靈
<lb n="0425a03"/>所俯仰。若有人能禮拜供養長壽福貴。不信
<lb n="0425a04"/>敬者運命不久。是以祿命書云。世有司命神
<lb n="0425a05"/>每至庚<note n="0425001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">申＝辛【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0425001"><lem>申</lem><rdg wit="【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">辛</rdg></app>日。上向天帝<note n="0425002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（所）＋陳【甲】</note><app n="0425002"><lem>陳</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">所陳</rdg></app>說眾人之罪惡。
<lb n="0425a06"/>重罪者則<note n="0425003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">徹＝撤【甲】【乙】，擲【丙】</note><note n="0425003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">徹＝撤【甲】【乙】，＝擲【丙】</note><app n="0425003"><lem>徹</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">撤</rdg><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">擲</rdg></app>算。輕罪者則去紀。算<note n="0425004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">書＝盡【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0425004"><lem>書</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">盡</rdg></app>紀<note n="0425005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">告即主＝告即至【甲】，失即至【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0425005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">告即主＝告即至【甲】，＝失即至【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0425005"><lem>告
<lb n="0425a07"/>即主</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">告即至</rdg><rdg wit="【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">失即至</rdg></app>命<note n="0425006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">已＝亡最好&M062403;【原】，亡【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0425006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">已＝亡最好&M062403;【原】，＝亡【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0425006"><lem>已</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">亡最好</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">亡</rdg></app>者。是故如來為末世薄福短命夭
<lb n="0425a08"/>死眾生故。說是一字頂輪王召北斗七星供
<lb n="0425a09"/>養護摩之儀則。為供養者。令其<note n="0425007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">屬命＝命屬【丙】</note><app n="0425007"><lem>屬命</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">命屬</rdg></app>星數削
<lb n="0425a10"/>死籍還付生籍。若諸國王於自宮中作曼茶
<lb n="0425a11"/>羅。如法護摩禮拜供養。北斗歡喜為擁護故。
<lb n="0425a12"/>久居勝位&M010527;受安穩。后妃夫人後宮<note n="0425008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">綵＝婇【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0425008"><lem>綵</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">婇</rdg></app>女。王
<lb n="0425a13"/>子群臣三公百官。上下和穆不行非法。人民
<lb n="0425a14"/>熾盛稼穡豐饒國土安寧。無有災難不現<note n="0425009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">怪異＝異怪【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0425009"><lem>怪
<lb n="0425a15"/>異</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">異怪</rdg></app>。疫病死<note n="0425010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">亡＝市【乙】</note><app n="0425010"><lem>亡</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">市</rdg></app>不起。境內怨敵群賊自然退
<lb n="0425a16"/>散。故以是法甚為祕要</p>
<lb n="0425a17"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead>北斗七<note n="0425011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">星＋（護摩）【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0425011"><lem>星</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">星護摩</rdg></app>祕要儀<note n="0425012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">軌＝則一卷【甲】</note><app n="0425012"><lem>軌</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">則一卷</rdg></app><note n="0425013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此下甲本奧書云久安四年七月二十八日於高野奉傳受了，乙本奧書云（朱書）嘉承二年二月十三日於禪定房以御本移點了同日御房受奉了，一校了僧林寬之本，久安五年二月二十一日辰時許樂生房奉受了僧&CB10923;信，丙本奧書云文和二年癸未二月二十七日申&CB00018;於神護寺成身院書寫畢宣澄二十四歲</note></jhead></juan></div1>
